WEBVTT

00:09.301 --> 00:11.759
You got any fresh coffee? Great.

00:13.349 --> 00:16.305
Carla, l hate to criticise,

00:16.478 --> 00:21.107
but l can't believe you actually read
these sleazy scandal sheets.

00:21.277 --> 00:24.729
Look at this. Even l'm above this.

00:24.907 --> 00:28.491
''Big Foot Stole My Wife.''

00:28.661 --> 00:31.579
''Have Aliens Taken Over Your Pet?''

00:31.749 --> 00:33.790
This is garbage!

00:34.879 --> 00:37.918
For your information,
l don't read those articles.

00:38.091 --> 00:40.334
l think they're just as stupid as you do.

00:40.512 --> 00:44.642
l get it because they happen to have
a great crossword puzzle.

00:44.810 --> 00:49.639
OK, let's see. Seven across.

00:49.816 --> 00:52.058
Five-headed cow born in Vermont.

00:54.364 --> 00:56.109
Maybelle.

00:57.576 --> 01:01.530
1 6 across.
State with the most UFO babies.

01:04.001 --> 01:08.583
- Arkansas.
- l don't believe it.

01:08.759 --> 01:13.803
32 across. The aphrodisiac
found in every kitchen cabinet.

01:15.767 --> 01:17.891
l don't know what that one is.

01:18.731 --> 01:21.353
Let me see what 1 4 down is.

01:21.527 --> 01:25.361
Where Franco's brain
is being kept alive.

01:25.532 --> 01:27.739
Fish tank.

01:28.911 --> 01:33.541
OK, so, the fifth letter
of the aphrodisiac is an A.

01:33.711 --> 01:37.080
Now l remember. Oregano.

01:39.759 --> 01:41.587
Trash.

